<br />\n坐位本身係好有學問<br />\nopen office最隱閉嘅位都係俾啲老屎忽坐<br />\n自己坐咩位 都睇到公司點對自己"},{"pid":"8cb3c0f74a1dbcd8179dad2cb2fa96ca1f52d3ef","tid":2271059,"uid":181819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"車文晶私家位"},{"pid":"067cef9d4293d8f7dde96b7b50059939802cce86","tid":2271059,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"出得人工夠高話之佢坐邊"},{"pid":"37ca56c1365d5fcf4fea7ef54601b16822ace98d","tid":2271059,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cc3e8ad78897d5f2f8caba445b311aed73f9c7a","tid":2271059,"uid":268516,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果人人都係咁, open office，咁就無得投訴<br />\n雖然我都好憎，例如工作經常要入password 或者有啲機密野要搞，一陣俾人望到又入自己數<br />\n<br />\n但如果人人都有partition 但有啲位寧捨開揚<br />\n咁多數呢啲位都係俾超低級職員坐，否則你問我，我第一日返工見到咁樣都會辭職，因為明顯係公司嘅地底泥<br />\n<br />\n坐位本身係好有學問<br />\nopen office最隱閉嘅位都係俾啲老屎忽坐<br />\n自己坐咩位 都睇到公司點對自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"感謝你詳細的回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好有心機<br />\n同意open office最隱閉嘅位都係俾啲老屎忽坐<br />\n<br />\n如果公同大部份同事都係平起平坐<br />\n個位零零舍舍開揚既位有機會係臨時加出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有機會比你遲入黎做唔洗坐果個位<br />\n低級過你既職員本身已坐緊正常位<br />\n<br />\n純粹係唔適合既時間入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9c14eff29b58b02f7336ffb76bf12def73a854","tid":2271059,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37ca56c1365d5fcf4fea7ef54601b16822ace98d","tid":2271059,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7cc3e8ad78897d5f2f8caba445b311aed73f9c7a","tid":2271059,"uid":268516,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果人人都係咁, open office，咁就無得投訴<br />\n雖然我都好憎，例如工作經常要